author: Matt Walsh
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, the Somali community in Minnesota rallies around a man who abducted and abused a child. They told the judge to go easy on him because he’s still getting accustomed to our “culture.” So what does that say about Somali culture? Also, several more states have now banned junk food from the food stamp program. We’ll talk about that and also the rise of so-called EBT influencers on TIkTok. It’s as horrible as it sounds. Plus, speaking of horrible, a former CNN anchor interviews an AI version of a child who died in a school shooting. Our dystopian future has arrived, and it’s somehow worse than anyone predicted.
